data.description: Data object containing parallel arrays `x` and `y`.

range.description:
The selected range, [start, end], for whichever axisType is chosen.
If axisType='x', it refers to x-values. If 'y', it refers to y-values.

axisType.description: Which axis this range is for: 'x' or 'y'.

setProps.description: A callback used to fire Dash events to update props

style.description: CSS style to apply to the container <div>.

className.description: Additional CSS classes for the container <div>.

lineStyle.description: Plotly line style for the main data trace.

grayZoneStyle.description: Plotly fill style for gray zones outside the selected range.

boundaryStyle.description: Plotly line style for the draggable boundaries.
